plets are due to l=1\nmodes. Attempts to reproduce the observed combination frequencies adopting all\npossible l=2 identifications for the triplets did not provide similarly\nconsistent results, supporting their identification with l=1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2002 12:00:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
